New Research Alert: The role of the data analyst is evolving‚Äîand AI is leading the charge.  

Alteryx‚Äôs latest global research report, "The 2025 State of Data Analysts in the Age of AI," reveals key insights shaping the future of analytics. Here‚Äôs what we found after surveying 1,400 data professionals across five industries: 
 
‚úîÔ∏è Strategic impact increasing ‚Äì 94% agree their role influences strategic decisions, and 87% report greater business impact in recent years. 
‚úîÔ∏è AI boosts productivity ‚Äì 7 out of 10 analysts say AI and automation make them more effective.  
‚úîÔ∏è Spreadsheet dependency persists ‚Äì 76% still rely on spreadsheets for data prep, with nearly half spending 6+ hours weekly on manual data cleaning.  
 
While analysts feel optimistic about the opportunities AI presents, the reliance on spreadsheets could threaten data quality and AI outcomes.  

Want to know how AI is transforming the analyst role‚Äîand how to stay ahead?  

Read the report here: https://ow.ly/3QjH30sK8TG
